Introduction

BABYS is a South Korean girl group that was previously a dance team formed in 2020. The group currently consists of Seoyu, Yeseo, and Suyeon. They made their debut on June 20, 2023 with the single album “Unlock It”.

The meaning of the name, “BABYS”, is to break away from bias and prejudice, aiming to express one’s pureness and freedom, just like a baby would.
